text: Mimolaia pichincha is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1992. It is known from Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Mimolaia pichincha. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1992
